HEADWORD: Slidometer
<hw>Sli*dom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Slide</ets> + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument
for indicating and recording shocks to railway cars occasioned by sudden
stopping.</def>⟦br⟧
